<li><a href="http://ohmyz.sh">Oh My Zsh</a> - An open source, community-driven framework for
managing your Zsh configuration.</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/sorin-ionescu/prezto">Prezto</a><a data-role="trackawesomelist-badge" href="https://github.com/sorin-ionescu/prezto" style="text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;"><span style="color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;"><span style="padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;">stars</span><span style="padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;">12.1k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{"type":"repo","stargazerCount":12066,"repo":"sorin-ionescu/prezto"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A speedy Zsh framework.
